findStrings.find: package com.peace.directed; import java.util.Stack; /** * Created by girishkumarbanda on 25/03/2017 AD. */ public class DirectedCycle { private boolean marked[]; private boolean onStack[]; private int [] edgeTo; private Stack<Integer> cycle; DirectedCycle(Digraph G,int s){ marked = new boolean[G.V()]; onStack = new boolean[G.V()]; edgeTo = new int [G.V()]; dfs(G,s); } private void dfs(Digraph G, int v) { marked[v] = true; onStack[v] = true; for (int w: G.adj(v)){ if (cycle !=null) return; if(!marked[w]){ marked[w] =true; edgeTo[w] =v; dfs(G,w); } else if(onStack[w]){ cycle = new Stack<>(); for (int x =v ; x!=w; x=edgeTo[x]){ cycle.push(x); } cycle.push(w); cycle.push(v); } } onStack[v] =false; } public Iterable<Integer> cycle(){ return cycle; } public boolean isCycle(){ return cycle !=null; } }
